Package: simplegwr
Title: A simple geographically weighted regression for teaching
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Urska", "Demsar", , "urska.demsar@st-andrews.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Package includes functions for a basic geographically weighted regression analysis, as normally used in undergraduate teaching. This includes a linear and a Poisson model and bandwidth optimisation for each.
